Question6

dataset_meal %>% ggplot() +  aes(x = main_dish, fill = main_dish) +   geom_bar() + labs(x = "Main Dish", y = "Count", title = "Main dish served and the method", subtitle = "Main Dish", caption = "main dish served and the method",  fill = "Legend")
